{
  "stem": "10162.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's just-- this was too well-planned for too long of a time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, it would take another couple of hours or maybe a day to just think of it that how, how-- well, this was a very civilized, highly industrialized nation.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And how they put all that know-how into-- for years, how many architects and scientists and who knows what, who, who-- what qualified learned people worked on, on on the perfection of such a, a machinery of killing off a whole race.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, you can imagine that they thought of that, that nobody can get out of there alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No way, no how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm glad you say that, because-- not in Auschwitz, not where I was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- there was no room for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the German factory, I think back of that sometimes, and I wish I could write because I would like to write just a short book on that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used to put on shows even there because the Germans wanted us-- when they found out there was somebody there who was a wonderful violinist and there was-- were a few who had beautiful voices.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was somebody who could play the piano very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were some girls who were acr-- great at acrobatics and ballet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "With a girlfriend, I used to put up-- we used to put up shows.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like we-- we were-- I remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was so funny.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were Antony and Cleopatra with some kind of a sheet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, we kind of took liberties with Shakespeare, you know, but the Germans didn't understand it anyway.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we made the scenery out of nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The, the poison that we had to fill the grenades and bombs with came in tall paper, double-thick paper bags.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When the paper bags emptied-- this is why we didn't freeze to death.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then we somehow cut up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- we didn't have scissors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't remember how, but we cut up shapes, and we put it in these wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I learned there how paper can keep you warm.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "What a wonderful insulating material it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And from the top, they used to pull out this pr-- the string.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there were several layers of string.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they started to knit from it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they were knitting little knee warmers and little socks and making very nice things that the Germans started to like, also-- the women who guarded us, the SS women.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's an interesting thing that I-- when I went to this reunion, and they introduced me to one of the girls I was going to grade school with, but we didn't recognize each other.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we asked a question from each other that everybody asked, I asked that, where did you work?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the grenades or bombs or upstairs or downstairs?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I s-- so I asked the same question.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She says, oh, I was in an aussenkommando.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, aussenkommando?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What's that?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said, well, we used to go out to dig.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, I didn't even know-- knew-- know that anybody ever went out to dig.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I thought everybody worked in the factories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She says, no, you remember that because I remember I-- we were going back and forth at yes, no, yes, no.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she says, no, you-- I know you did because I remember I was coming back one day, and I was said it was so hard because the, the, the earth is so hard to dig into because it's full of something like clay.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you said, clay?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And could you bring me some?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I brought you some.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And you were working this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had no recollection.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then it came back because others also said, yes, don't you remember?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was my birthday, and I was crying for my dead piano.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you made me a little piano.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then I started to remember that the German women kept asking me to make a little dog and a cat and a this and a that, and they would give us a half a potato or, or something for it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I was doing that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was doing this clay sculpture there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then once I was in, in, in the lagerspital because a grenade fell on my foot and broke it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was lying between two girls who were in much worse shape than I was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were these very cadaverous little things that couldn't even get out of bed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But one of them could speak.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was very-- a wonderful, lovely young woman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think she must have been maybe 20 or 21, and she was a teacher.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she knew a lot of poems.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she knew some poets I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
